corpse reviver
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an alchoholic pick-me-up drink; a first drink to dispel a hangover; the `hair of the dog'; G.J.Griffiths notes: liquor name; not quoted, but McHutcheson has added pencil quotes in his copy to show colloquialism; US context
